page-apps-collectibles-benefits-1-descri: Mgbe e mere ka ọrụ nka dị na tokin n'Ethereum, e nwere ike igosi onye nwe ya ka mmadụ niile hụ. I nwere ike ịchọpụta njem ọrụ nka site n'okike gaa na onye ji ya ugbua. Nke a na-egbochi nṅomi.
page-apps-collectibles-benefits-1-title: Onwunwe bụ ihe nwere ihe nrita
page-apps-collectibles-benefits-2-descri: Ikwụ ụgwọ ige egwu n'ịntanetị maọbụ zụta ihe nke ọrụ nka dị mma karịa ndị na-ese ihe. N'Ethereum e ọ adịchaghị ka e nwee ndị nnonetiti na-agba etiti. Ma ọ bụrụ na a chọghị ndị nnọnetiti, ụgwọ ha adịghị elu n'ihi na nhiwe dị elu ekwesịghị ịkwu ụgwọ maka akụrụngwa nke netwọkụ.
page-apps-collectibles-benefits-3-descri: E tinyere akụrụngwa ndị e ji tokin egote n'adreesị Ethereum gị, ọ bụghị na nke nhiwe. Ya bụ, i nwere ike ire ihe dị ka akụrụngwa onyoonyoo n'ebe azụmahịa Ethereum ọbụla, ọ bụghị sọọsọ naanị n'akụrụngwa onyonyo n'onwe ya.
page-apps-collectibles-benefits-4-descri: Ngwa ọrụ na ngwaahịa dị adị ka ị wee jiri tokin tokin gota ọrụ nka gị ma ree ya! Ma e nwere ike ire tokin gi na na nke ọbụla nakwa na nhiwe ihe owuwe Ethereum ndị.
page-apps-collectibles-benefits-descript: Ndị a bụ ngwa na-ele anya n'inwe dijitalụ, na-ewelite ego nrita maka ndị nkepụta, ma na-achọpụtakwa ụzọ ọhụrụ ị ga-eji tụnyere onye nkepụta na ọrụ ha kacha masị gị.
page-apps-collectibles-benefits-title: ihe orire na-achịkwa onwe ya na ige egwu
page-apps-collectibles-description: Ndị a bụ ngwa na-ele anya n'inwe dijitalụ, na-ewelite ego nrita maka ndị nkepụta, ma na-achọpụtakwa ụzọ ọhụrụ ị ga-eji tụnyere onye nkepụta na ọrụ ha kacha masị gị.
page-apps-collectibles-title: Ihe mmepụta a naghị achịkwa na ihe orire
page-apps-dapp-description-1inch: Na-enyere gị aka izere ọnụahịa ịrị elu sitere n'ikpokọta ọnụahịa nke kacha mma.
page-apps-dapp-description-aave: Gbazinye tokin gị ka i nweta ọmụrụnwa ma werekwa ya mgbe ọbụla.
page-apps-dapp-description-async-art: Mepụta, nakọta, ma zụọ ahịa #ProgrammableArt - eserese dijitalụ e tinyere n' “Ebe Nhazi” nke i nwere ike iji mezie ihe onyonyo niile. Masta Ebe Nhazi ọbụla bụ akpa ego ERC721.
page-apps-dapp-description-audius: Ebe nhiwe ige egwu n'ịntanetị enweghị nchịkwa. Na-ege = ego maka ndị mmepụta, ọ bụghị labelụ.
page-apps-dapp-description-augur: Tinye ego n'egwuregwu, akụ na ụba, nakwa emume ndị ọzọ dị n'ụwa.
page-apps-dapp-description-axie-infinity: Gbanwee ma lụso ihe nkepụta a kpọrọ Axies ọgụ. Na-eritakwa ego mgbe ị na-etinye ego - nke a dị na mobaịl
page-apps-dapp-description-balancer: Balansa bụ nke na-eji aka ya hazie onwe ya na ebe nhiwe azụmahịa kripto.
page-apps-dapp-description-brave: Nweta tokin maka ime nchọgharị ma jirikwa ya kwadoo ndị nkepụta kacha masị gị.
page-apps-dapp-description-cent: Netwọk ọha ebe ị na-erita ego site n'ibiputa NFT.
page-apps-dapp-description-compound: Gbazinye tokin gị ka i nweta ọmụrụnwa ma werekwa ya mgbe ọbụla.
page-apps-dapp-description-cryptopunks: Zụta, kwee ọnụ, nyekwa ọtụtụ akụrụngwa maka orire - otu n'ime tokin ihe orire nke mbụ n'Ethereum.
page-apps-dapp-description-cryptovoxels: Meputa ebe nhiwe ọrụ nka, rụọ ụlọ a na-ere ahịa, ma zụta ala - nke nnọchiteanya ihe na-eme n'ụwa n'Ethereum.
page-apps-dapp-description-dark-forest: Zuo ụwa niile ọnụ, n'usoro n'usoro, nke e nwetara site na nke kripto seputara.
page-apps-dapp-description-decentraland: Nata, ree ala n'ịntanetị ma mee nchọpụta.
page-apps-dapp-description-ens: Aha dị mfe ojiji maka adreesị na saịtị anaghị achịkwa.
page-apps-dapp-description-foundation: Tinye ego na mbipụta pụrụ iche nke dijitalụ ọrụ nka ma soro ndị ọzọ na-azụta ahịa mee mgbanwe.
page-apps-dapp-description-gitcoin: Nweta kripto na-arụ ọrụ na ngwanrọ mepere emepe.
page-apps-dapp-description-gitcoin-grant: Iji nnakọta ego ehiwere ọfụma nakọta ego maka ọrụ otu Ethereum
page-apps-dapp-description-gods-unchaine: Kaadị azụmahịa egwuregwu nwere usoro. Nweta kaadị site n'itinye na i nwere ike ire n'ezie.
page-apps-dapp-description-golem: Nweta ike kọmpụta e kọrịtara maọbụ gbazinye ihe nke gị.
page-apps-dapp-description-radicle: Chekwaa koodu ndị otu n'enweghị ndị nnọnetiti.
page-apps-dapp-description-loopring: Ebe azụmahịa ọgbọ na ọgbọ a rụrụ ka ọ na-aga ngwa ngwa.
page-apps-dapp-description-marble-cards: Mepụta ma zụọ kaadị dijitalụ pụrụ iche dabere na URL.
page-apps-dapp-description-matcha: Na-achọ ọtụtụ mgbanwe iji nye aka chọtara gị ọnụ ahịa kacha mma.
page-apps-dapp-description-nifty-gateway: Zụrụ ọrụ onye na onye site n'aka ndị ọrụ nka, ndị na-eme asọmpi egwuregwu, ndị ejije a ma ama.
page-apps-dapp-description-oasis: Zụọ ahịa, gbazitere ego, ma jiri Dai, stebụlkọịn nke Ethereum, chekwaa ego.
page-apps-dapp-description-opensea: Zụrụ, ree, chọpụta ma zụọ ngwa ahịa nwere oke.
page-apps-dapp-description-opera: Si na ngwa nchọgharị gị zigara onye ahịa kripto, ndị ojiji na ngwa ndị ọzọ.
page-apps-dapp-description-poap: Chịkọta NFT na-egosi na ị nọ na mmemme dị iche iche n'ịntanetị maọbụ na mmadụ. Jiri ha sonyere rafụlụ, vootuo, mekọrịta, maọbụ naanị ịṅa isi.
page-apps-dapp-description-polymarket: Tinye ego na nsonaazụ. Zụọ ahịa n'ozi ahịa.
page-apps-dapp-description-pooltogether: Lọtrị ị gaghị atụfu. Ihe nrite kwa izu.
page-apps-dapp-description-index-coop: Ego ntinye kripto nke na-eweputa pọtụfoliyo gị na DeFi a ma ama.
page-apps-dapp-description-nexus-mutual: Mkpuchi na-enweghị ụlọ ọrụ mkpuchi. Nweta nchekwa nyere nsogbu ngwa kọmputa nakwa igbanwe koodu.
page-apps-dapp-description-etherisc: Ụdị mkpuchi dịịrị onwe ya nke onye ọbụla nwere ike iji mepụta mkpuchi nke ha.
page-apps-dapp-description-zapper: Sochie pọtụfoliyo gị wee jiri ụdị ngwaahịa DeFi sitere n'otu njikọ.
page-apps-dapp-description-zerion: Jikwaa pọtụfoliyo gị ma nyochaa ngwaahịa DeFi ọbụla n'ahịa.
page-apps-dapp-description-rotki: Mepee ebe nsochi pọtụfoliyo, Pọtụfoliyo mepere emepe, nnyocha, ndekọ na ngwaọrụ ndekọ ụtụ nke na-akpahapụrụ ihe nzuzo gị anya.
page-apps-dapp-description-krystal: Nhiwe na-enye ndị ahịa ihe ha chọrọ n'otu oge iji nweta ikike na ọrụ DeFi kacha masị gị.
page-apps-dapp-description-rarible: Mepụta, ree ma zụta ihe orire tokin.
page-apps-dapp-description-sablier: Kirie ego n'ịntanetị mgbe o kwesiri.
page-apps-dapp-description-superrare:
Si n'aka onye ọrụ nka zụta ọrụ nka dijitalụ
 maọbụ n'aha onye ọzọ na-ere ha n'ahịa.
page-apps-dapp-description-token-sets: Atụmatụ itinye ego nke kripto nke na-emezigharị na-akaghị ya aka.
page-apps-dapp-description-uniswap: Gbanwee kokin maọbụ weta tokin maka pasenti nkwụghachi ụgwọ.
page-apps-dapp-description-dexguru: Ngwụcha azumahia na-enweghi onye ndú maka ndị ahia DeFi
page-apps-dapp-description-synthetix: Sintetiks bụ usoro e ji enye ma na-ere ngwaahịa sintetiks
page-apps-docklink-smart-contracts: Nkwekọrịta azụmahịa na emere onwe ya
page-apps-editors-choice-dark-forest: Rụo ndị ọzọ ụka tinye ego ka ị zuo ụwa ọnụ ma gbaa mbọ na-emelite teknụzụ Ethereum. Ikekwa ọ bụrụ otu maka ndị ahụ maka ndị ahụ ma Ethereum ọfụma.
page-apps-editors-choice-description: Obere dapp nke ndi oru ethereum.org na-ahu n'anya ugbua. Tulee dapp ndi ozo n'okpuru.
page-apps-editors-choice-foundation: Tinye ego na omenaala. Zụta, tinye ego, ma rekwaa dijitalụ ọrụ nka na fashịọn pụrụ iche sitere na ezigbote ndị ọrụ nka, ndị egwu, nakwa ụdị.
page-apps-editors-choice-pooltogether: Zuta tiket maka lọtrị atụfua. Izu uka obula, a na-ezigara onye meriri ọmụrụnwa e nwetara na puulu tiketi. Nwetaghachi ego gị mbe ọbụla ị chọrọ.
page-apps-editors-choice-uniswap: Gbanwee tokin gi n'egbughị oge. Otu kach nwee mmasị nke na-enye ohere ijiri ndị menyi nọ na netwọk ebe niile ree tokin.
page-apps-explore-dapps-description: A ka ji ọtụtụ dapp ama atu, na-enyocha ma netwọk ya o nwere ike ịrụ n'onwe ya. Mana e nwere ọtụtụ ihe gara nke ọma na teknụzụ mbido ya, ego, egwuregwu nakwa ụdị ihe ndị a na-ere ere.
page-apps-features-1-description: Ozugbo e zigara ya n'Ethereum, e nweghị ike iwepu koodu dapp. Ma onye ọbụla nwere ike iji akụrụngwa dapp ahụ. Ọ bụrụgodị na otu na-ahụ maka dapp ahụ etisaa, ị ka nwekwara ike ị na-eji ya eme ihe. Ozugbo ọ dị n'Ethereum, ọ ga-anogide ebe ahụ.
page-apps-features-2-description: A gaghị egbochinwuru gị iji dapp ahụ maọbụ inyefe azumahia gi. Iji maa atụ, ọ bụrụ na Twịta dị n'Ethereum, o nweghị onye ọbụla ga-egbochinwu akaụntụ gị maọbụ kwụsị ide ihe na Twịta.
page-apps-features-3-description: N'ihi n'Ethereum nwere ETH, ịkwụ ụgwọ bụ eze a ma na-aga echi n'Ethereum. Onye nupụta agaghị egbu oge ịhụ na ya na ndị ọzọ na-ahụ maka ikwu ụgwọ na-arụkọtaoru.
page-apps-features-4-description: Koodu dapp na-adịkarị n'ebe mmepe ma dabakwa na ndakọrịta. Ndị otu na-eji ọrụ ndị otu ọzọ ewunyite. Ọ bụrụ na ị chọrọ ime ka ndị ojiji gbanwee tokin ndapp gị, i nwere ike tinye koodu dapp ọzọ.
page-apps-features-5-description: Site n'ọtụtụ dapp, i kwesịghị ikekọrịta ezigbo njirimara. Akaụntụ Ethereum gị bụ nbanye gị ma i kwesiri inwe akpa ego ịntanetị.
page-apps-features-6-description: Kriptografi na-ahụ na ndị nwakpo enweghị ike ime nṅomị asị maka azụmahịa nakwa mmekọrịta dapp ndị ọzọ n'aha gị. Ị na-eji akaụntụ Ethereum gi enye dapp ikike ihe ọ ga-eme - nke na-abụkarị na akpa ego ịntanetị gị - ka akwụkwọ gị nwee gị nwee nchekwa.
page-apps-features-7-description: Ozugbo dapp dị na Ethereum, ọ ga-agbada ma ọ bụrụ na Ethereum n'onwe ya na-agbada. Netwọk nha nke cEthereum bụ nke siri ike ịwakpo.
page-apps-finance-benefits-1-description: Ọrụ ego n'Ethereum enweghị ihe ndebanye aha a chọrọ. Ọ bụrụ na i nwere ego ma nwee njikọ ịntanetị, i nwere ike isonye.
page-apps-finance-benefits-2-description: E nwere ọtụtụ tokin i nwere ike ịga na ya n'akụrụngwa ego ndị a. Ndị mmadụ na-arụ tokin ọhụrụ n'Ethereum mgbe ọbụla.
page-apps-finance-benefits-3-description: Otu dị iche iche rụpụtala stebụlkọịn - cryptocurrency na-adịghị agbanwe agbanwe. Ndị a na-enye gị ohere ịnwale nakwa iji crypto na-enweghị ihe ize ndụ e jighị n'aka.
page-apps-finance-benefits-3-title: Crptocurrency ana etinye na udi aku ndi ozo
page-apps-finance-benefits-4-description: Ego ngwaahịa na nhiwe Ethereum bụ mọdụla. ma so kwara ndị ọzọ daba. Nhazi ọhụrụ nke modul ndị a na-ewu ahịa mgbe niile, na-abawanye ihe i nwere ike iji crypto gị mee.
page-apps-finance-benefits-description: Kedu ihe ahụ dị n'Ethereum nke na-enye ohere ka ngwa ego na-aga nke ọma?
page-apps-finance-benefits-title: ego nke na-enweghị onye isi nduzi
page-apps-finance-description: E nwere ọtụtụ ngwa na-eleba anya n'iji cryptocurrencies rụpụta ọrụ ego. Ha na-enye ìhè dị ka ịgbazinye ego, ibinye ego, irita eog ọmụrụnwa, nakwa ịkwụ ụgwọ onwe - enweghị data nkeonwe a chọrọ.
page-apps-finance-title: Ego na-enweghị onye na-achịkwa ya nọ n'isi
page-apps-gaming-benefits-1-description: Maọbụ ala dị n'ịntanetị maọbụ kaadị azụmaahịa, e nwere ike ree akụrụngwa gị n'ahịa ihe oriri. Akụrụngwa dị a na-eme na kọmputa nyere ọnụahịa dịka nke dị n'ụlọ uwa.
page-apps-gaming-benefits-1-title: Ihe egwuregwu gbara ọtụtụ ka token
page-apps-gaming-benefits-2-description: Na ngwaahịa gị, nakwa mgbe ụfọdụ n'ọganihu gị, ọ bụghị ụlọ ọrụ egwuregwu. Ya bụ na ọ gaghị efu gị ihe ọbụla ma ọ bụrụ na a wakporo ụlọ ọrụ na-ahụ maka egwuregwu ahụ, nwee nsogbu nke sava, maọbụ gbasasịa.
page-apps-gaming-benefits-3-description: N'otu aka ahụ ịkwụ ụgwọ Ethereum si dị ka onye ọbụla nyochaa, egwuregwu nwere ike iji nke a mee ka ọ dị mma. Na nkọwa, e nwere ike ime nnyocha ihe site n'ọnụọgụ nke siri ike rue na etu ike ndị na-agbaso mgba ha.
page-apps-gaming-benefits-3-title: Ezi omume a ma na o ziri ezi
page-apps-gaming-benefits-description: Kedu ihe ahụ gbasara Ethereum nke na-eme ka egwuregwu kọmputa na-aga nke ọma?
page-apps-gaming-benefits-title: egwuregwu kọmputa nke na-enweghị onye isi nduzi
page-apps-gaming-description: Ndị a bụ ngwa na-elekwasị anya n'ichepụta ihe na-eme n'ụwa ịntanetị ma jiri ihe owuwe nwere ezigbo ọnụahịa na-alụsokwa otu ọzọ ọgụ.
page-apps-gaming-title: Egwuregwu kọmputa na-enweghị onye isi nduzi
page-apps-get-some-eth-description: Ihe a na-eme na dapp na-ewe ego azụmahịa
page-apps-get-started-subtitle: Iji nwalee dapp, ị ga-enwe akpa ego ịntanetị na ETH. Akpa ego ịntanetị ga-eme ka i jikọọ, maọbụ banye. I kwesikwara inwe ETH iji kwụọ ụgwọ azụmahịa ọbụla.
page-apps-hero-header: Ngwaọrụ na ọrụ nke Ethereum kwadoro
page-apps-hero-subtitle: Dapps bụ ngwa ngagharị na-eto eto nke na-eji Ethereum na-mebie ụdị azụmaahịa maọbụ na-emepụta nke ọhụrụ.
page-apps-how-dapps-work-p1: Dapps nwere koodu dị n'ime (ngwa kọmputa) na-arụ ọrụ na netwọk enweghị onye isi nduzi ma ọ bụghị nke nwere onye isi nduzi. Ha na-eji blọkchen Ethereum ahụ maka nchebe data yana ngwa kọmputa maka ngwa ljik ha.
page-apps-how-dapps-work-p2: Ngwa kọmputa dị ka usoro iwu nke dị na chen ka mmadụ niile hụ ma gbasoro usoro iwu ndị ahụ. Were ya na ọ bụ igwe na-ere ahịa: ọ bụrụ na i nye ya ego zuru oke yana nhọrọ ziri ezi, ị ga-enweta ihe ị chọrọ. Ma dị ka igwe na-ere ahịa, ngwa kọmputa nwere ike ijide ego dị ka akaụntụ Ethereum gị. Nke a na-enye ohere ka koodù nwee nkwekọrịta a mee azụmahịa.
page-apps-how-dapps-work-p3: Ozugbo e tinyere dapps na netwọk Ethereum, i nweghị ike ịgbanwe ha. E nwere ike ime ka dapps ghara inwe onye isi nduzi n'ihi na a na-achịkwa ya site n'echiche e dere na nkwekọrịta, ọ bụghị nkeonwe maọbụ ụlọ ọrụ.
page-apps-learn-callout-description: Pọtalụ otu mmepụta anyị nwere docs, ngwaọrụ, yana usoro ọrụ iji nyere gị aka ịmalite iwu dapp.
page-apps-learn-callout-image-alt: Ọmụmatụ nke aka na-ewu akara ETH site na brik lego.
page-apps-learn-callout-title: Mụta ka e si arụ dapp
page-apps-magic-behind-dapps-description: Dapps nwere ike ịdị ka ngwa ndị ọzọ. Mana n'azie, ha nwere ụfọdụ akụrụngwa pụrụ iche n'ihi na ha na-enweta ikike Ethereum niile. Nke a bụ ihe na-eme ka dapps dị iche na ngwa ndị ọzọ.
page-apps-magic-behind-dapps-link: Kedu ihe na-eme ka Ethereum bụrụ ọpụrụiche?
page-apps-magic-behind-dapps-title: Ihe ndị na-eme ka dapps bụrụ ọpụrụiche
page-apps-poap-logo-alt: Akara ngosi Usoro Iheakebe nke Ọbịbịa (Poap)
page-apps-set-up-a-wallet-description: Akpa ego intaneti bụ "nbanye" gị maka dapp
page-apps-technology-description: Ndị a bụ ngwa na-elekwasị anya n'ime ka ngwaọrụ onye mmeputa ghara inwe onye ise nduzi, na-etinye usoro akụ na ụba crypto na teknụzụ dị ugbua, ma na emepụtakwa ebe azụmaahịa maka ọrụ mpepe a ma ebe ha si.
page-apps-wallet-callout-description: Akpa ego ịntanetị bụkwa dapps. Chọta otu dabere na ngwaọrụ masịrị gị.
page-apps-warning-header: Hụ na ị na-e me nnyocha nke gị mgbe niile
page-apps-warning-message: Ethereum bụ teknụzụ ọhụrụ na ọtụtụ ngwa dị ọhụrụ. Tupu itinye ego ọbụla buru ibu, jide n'aka na ị ghọtara ọghọm dị na ya.
page-apps-more-on-defi-button: Ihe ndị ọzọ gbasara ego na-enweghị onye isi nduzi
